data.description: This home will not disappoint. Open floor plan with updated eat in kitchen with large island. Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, vinyl flooring. Kitchen opens up to cozy family room. Three bedrooms, Great storage. Finished basement for extra living space. Large fenced in backyard with deck to enjoy the outdoors. Great location and close to highways and shopping.
